As the IL concentration increases, ??  values become more negative because 
the enthalpy change decreases and the entropy change increases. Based on the mechanism 

proposed for SDS-IL interactions, the enthalpic stabilization promoted by the presence 

of ILs on the micellization process (?? &lt;) is due to the following reasons: (i) the 
IL promotes electrostatic shielding that decreases the electrostatic repulsion energy 

